	<h1 class="title">竹材走俏，除了做灯，它还能做什么？｜2015 上海国际家具展</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-10 14:17:45 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14738/medium/14738.jpg?1441857207" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


